ACTION REQUIRED: Approve Monthly Invoice
=========================================

Customer: <%= @user&.first_name %> <%= @user&.last_name %> (<%= @user&.email %>)
Subscription: <%= @subscription.plan %> — <%= @subscription.duration %>-month contract
Installment: <%= @installment_number %> of <%= @subscription.duration %>

Line Items
----------
<% @invoice.invoice_items.each do |item| %>
  <%= item.product&.title %> x<%= item.quantity %> — R<%= number_with_precision((item.amount.to_f * item.quantity.to_f), precision: 2) %>
<% end %>

TOTAL: R<%= number_with_precision(@invoice.total_amount.to_f, precision: 2) %>
Due: <%= @invoice.due_date&.strftime('%-d %b %Y') %>

Approve & send to customer:
<%= @approve_url %>

This invoice will NOT be sent until you click the link above.
